text: Dzhurak () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Astrakhansky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 214 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 75 km from Astrakhan, 80 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Dzhurak
